overview.title: Clubs Exchange: Neon Party
overview.excerpt: Join us for the Neon Party to meet members from other clubs, dance, and enjoy a vibrant night out.

details.title: Clubs Exchange: Neon Party
details.longDescription: Come to the Clubs Exchange: Neon Party for a night of music, dancing, and socializing! This is a great chance to meet members from other clubs, enjoy a lively neon-themed atmosphere, and have fun with your friends.
